I am giving you the
opportunity of a lifetime.

00:22:25.544 --> 00:22:26.611 line:95%,end
OK.

00:22:26.678 --> 00:22:28.947 line:95%,end
You will be performing in the
Sunday matinee at 12:00 noon.

