routine, "Sugar Babies."

00:26:09.301 --> 00:26:11.703 line:95%,end
it's fun. It's comic relief.

00:26:11.903 --> 00:26:15.340 line:95%,end
This is the best opportunity
for these girls to shine.

00:26:16.141 --> 00:26:19.578 line:95%,end
At this point in the season,
they should be at their peak.

00:26:19.778 --> 00:26:22.013 line:95%,end
I almost forgot about this
whole photo shoot thing.

