ABBY: Come on.

00:26:32.591 --> 00:26:33.725 line:95%,end
-Ah!
-All right.

00:26:34.859 --> 00:26:36.328 line:95%,end
Abby doesn't even know
who's on the cover.

00:26:36.394 --> 00:26:37.529 line:95%,end
I don't.

00:26:37.596 --> 00:26:41.933 line:95%,end
So we came to the Abby Lee Dance
Company specifically to find

00:26:42.367 --> 00:26:48.573 line:95%,end
